      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> over a medium heat</p><p>Once hot, add the<strong> sliced spring onion </strong>with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and cook for 1-2 min or until softened</p><p>Add the <strong>vegetable stock</strong>,<strong> soft cheese</strong> and a generous grind of <strong>black pepper </strong>and cook for 2-3 min or until starting to thicken – this is your<strong> creamy sauce</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
