    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, strip your <strong>mint</strong> <strong>leaves</strong> from their stems and chop them finely, discard the stems</p><p>Wash your <strong>salad</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Add the<strong> salad</strong> and <strong>tomato wedges</strong> to a bowl with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong>, a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and a<strong> </strong>grind of <strong>black pepper</strong> and mix everything together – this is your <strong>leafy tomato salad</strong></p>",
