      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>creamy pea & sugar snap farfalle </strong>with the<strong> leafy tomato salad </strong>to the side</p><p>Sprinkle over the <strong>remaining grated Italian hard cheese</strong> and garnish with the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>chopped mint</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
